{"title":"Distributable profits of long-term (life) insurers","public_updated_at":"2016-12-09T15:49:33Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>This consultation seeks views on technical changes to the legal definition of life insurers’ distributable profits. This definition affects how life insurers’ calculate the profits available for distribution to their shareholders.</p>\n\n<p>The changes are needed to update the law in order to reflect changes to the regulation of life insurers.</p>\n\n<p>This issue will be of interest to relevant specialists in the life insurance industry, investors in life insurers, and their advisers.</p>\n</div>","closing_date":"2016-11-16T00:00:00.000+00:00","emphasised_organisations":["1994e0e4-bd19-4966-bbd7-f293d6e90a6b"],"opening_date":"2016-10-25T15:30:00.000+01:00","change_history":[{"public_timestamp":"2016-12-09T15:49:33.000+00:00","note":"Updated with consultation summary."},{"public_timestamp":"2016-10-26T12:51:55.000+01:00","note":"Amended: Question 4a referenced the wrong section in the draft regulations. This has now been changed."},{"public_timestamp":"2016-10-25T15:30:00.000+01:00","note":"First published."}],"documents":["<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_1856741\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/562916/distributable_profits_consultation_final.pdf\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/562916/thumbnail_distributable_profits_consultation_final.pdf.png\" /></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/562916/distributable_profits_consultation_final.pdf\">Distributable profits of long-term (life) insurers: a consultation</a></h2>\n    <p class=\"metadata\">\n        <span class=\"references\">\n          Ref: ISBN <span class=\"isbn\">978-1-911375-28-9</span>, <span class=\"unique_reference\">PU1975</span>\n        </span>\n        <span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">459KB</span>, <span class=\"page-length\">23 pages</span>\n    </p>\n\n\n  </div>\n</section>"],"final_outcome_detail":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The government would like to thank stakeholders for their responses to this consultation.</p>\n\n<p>Given the overwhelming feedback stating an updated framework for distributions of insurance companies should be in place before the end of 2016, the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2016/1194/contents/made\">statutory instrument</a> effecting the changes has been made and was laid before Parliament on 8 December.</p>\n</div>","first_public_at":"2016-10-25T15:30:00.000+01:00","political":true,"government":{"title":"2015 Conservative government","slug":"2015-conservative-government","current":true},"tags":{"browse_pages":[],"policies":[],"topics":[]}},"routes":[{"path":"/government/consultations/distributable-profits-of-long-term-life-insurers","type":"exact"}],"redirects":[],"publishing_app":"whitehall","rendering_app":"whitehall-frontend","need_ids":[],"phase":"live","analytics_identifier":null,"document_type":"consultation_outcome","schema_name":"consultation","first_published_at":"2016-10-25T14:35:23Z","base_path":"/government/consultations/distributable-profits-of-long-term-life-insurers","description":"Seeking views on technical changes to the legal definition of life insurers’ distributable profits.","content_id":"14835c29-04a9-439a-9ebe-bebeb36c9604","locale":"en","expanded_links":{"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D15","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/hm-treasury","base_path":"/government/organisations/hm-treasury","content_id":"1994e0e4-bd19-4966-bbd7-f293d6e90a6b","description":null,"document_type":"organisation","locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2016-03-22T14:52:15Z","s